"title": "8441: goals",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8441",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Jesus Christ's basic aim was to do his Father's will. Believers have the same objective, which Jesus Christ and the Holy Spirit enable them to achieve.</p>\n<h2>God's goals</h2>\n<h3>To live with his people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:11-Lev26:12\">LEV 26:11–26:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps23:6\">PSA 23:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech2:10\">ZEC 2:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:23\">JHN 14:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:3\">REV 21:3</a></p>\n<h3>To build his church in Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:18\">MAT 16:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:19-Eph2:22\">EPH 2:19–2:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:2\">REV 21:2</a></p>\n<h3>To perfect his church in Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:26-Eph5:27\">EPH 5:26–5:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps138:8\">PSA 138:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:6\">PHP 1:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:10\">COL 2:10</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's goals</h2>\n<h3>To do his Father's will</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:38\">JHN 6:38</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:39\">MAT 26:39</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:36\">MRK 14:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:42\">LUK 22:42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:34\">JHN 4:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:30\">JHN 5:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:7\">HEB 10:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:9\">HEB 10:9</a></p>\n<h3>To preach the gospel</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:43\">LUK 4:43</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:38\">MRK 1:38</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:18-Luke4:19\">LUK 4:18–4:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:1-Isa61:2\">ISA 61:1–61:2</a></p>\n<h3>To save the lost</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:10\">LUK 19:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:21-Matt15:28\">MAT 15:21–15:28</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:24-Mark7:30\">MRK 7:24–7:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:7\">LUK 15:7</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:14\">MAT 18:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:10\">LUK 15:10</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ achieved his goals</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:4\">JHN 17:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:32\">LUK 13:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:31\">JHN 12:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:28\">JHN 19:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:30\">JHN 19:30</a></p>\n<h2>Believers' goals</h2>\n<h3>To please God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:9\">2CO 5:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:18\">ROM 14:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:10\">EPH 5:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:17\">EPH 5:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:9-Col1:10\">COL 1:9–1:10</a></p>\n<h3>To know God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:8\">PHP 3:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:3\">JHN 17:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:10\">PHP 3:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:18\">2PE 3:18</a></p>\n<h3>To be faithful to Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:4\">JHN 15:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:22\">MAT 10:22</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:13\">MRK 13:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:13\">MAT 24:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:14\">PHP 3:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:7\">2TI 4:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:2\">HEB 12:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:26\">REV 2:26</a></p>\n<h3>To love one another</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:34\">JHN 13:34</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:34-Matt22:40\">MAT 22:34–22:40</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:28-Mark12:31\">MRK 12:28–12:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:25-Luke10:28\">LUK 10:25–10:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:12\">JHN 15:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor13:13\">1CO 13:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor16:14\">1CO 16:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:5\">1TI 1:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:11-1John4:12\">1JN 4:11–4:12</a></p>\n<h3>To live at peace</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:18\">ROM 12:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:50\">MRK 9:50</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor13:11\">2CO 13:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:11\">1TH 4:11</a></p>\n<h3>To spread the gospel</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:19-Matt28:20\">MAT 28:19–28:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:24\">ACT 20:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:14\">ROM 11:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:20\">ROM 15:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor9:16\">1CO 9:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:2\">2TI 4:2</a></p>\n<h3>To grow to maturity</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:13\">EPH 4:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:48\">MAT 5:48</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:29\">ROM 8:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:18\">2CO 3:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor7:1\">2CO 7:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor13:11\">2CO 13:11</a></p>\n<h3>Believers' final goal is heaven</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:9-Rev7:10\">REV 7:9–7:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:40\">JHN 6:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:51-1Cor15:52\">1CO 15:51–15:52</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:4-2Cor5:5\">2CO 5:4–5:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:17\">1TH 4:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:2\">1JN 3:2</a></p>\n<h3>God guarantees that believers will reach their goal</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:2-John14:3\">JHN 14:2–14:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:39\">JHN 6:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:38-Rom8:39\">ROM 8:38–8:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:13-Eph1:14\">EPH 1:13–1:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:6\">PHP 1:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:12\">2TI 1:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:11-2Tim2:13\">2TI 2:11–2:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:5\">REV 3:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:21\">REV 3:21</a></p>",
